title: Japanese Prints Playing Cards
description:
Japanese Prints stunned van Gogh and the Impressionists with their vibrancy and focus on line and color. The celebration of simple things like snow and blossom inspired a return to nature. These prints honor the genius of artists like Hokusai and Hiroshige whose compositional bravado changed art forever.
  • Dimensions: 2.63 x 0.75 x 3.63 in
  • Materials: Single poker size deck of playing cards featuring images of Japanese prints.
